Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.20,0:00:17.67,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:24.16,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free to consider me your enemy, hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:28.10,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,She destroyed that Soul Eater in one hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.10,0:00:30.21,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,How overpowered can you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:32.98,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stop trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:35.71,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Naofumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.02,0:00:38.72,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:43.81,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Now, shall we begin
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:46.67,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,the true battle of the Wave?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.38,sign_3370_33_The_Rising_of_th,OP Card,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(750,645)}The Rising of the Shield Hero
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:33.85,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to attack, Hero Naofumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:36.71,sign_5367_37_Lullaby_at_Dawn,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(486,682)}The Raven Invader
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.85,0:02:37.04,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Why not send those servants of yours at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:39.19,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Servants?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.19,0:02:40.52,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just call us...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.52,0:02:41.67,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,...Naofumi's servants?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.90,0:02:43.33,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.56,0:02:59.87,main,Ren,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor Slash!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.26,main,Mot,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor Thrust!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:02.40,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor Shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.69,0:03:18.74,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all you've got?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:25.38,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Zero-Stance Rondo: Reverse Four Seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:39.23,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,So you are but mere servants.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:41.94,main,Its,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-She's strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:46.74,sign_7295_24_Soul_Soothing_Po,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(397,10}Soul Soothing Potion—Effect: SP Recovery
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.65,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll entertain me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.70,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm no entertainer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:55.08,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.86,0:04:01.00,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:16.36,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think this feeble \Nvenom could put defeat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.15,0:04:17.82,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.82,0:04:19.57,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,High Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.93,0:04:24.19,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Eight kicks in a single instant? \NHow very admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.19,0:04:26.20,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,But they cannot touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.73,0:04:32.84,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Not even worthy of mention.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:42.18,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Both of you, get behind me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.03,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.74,0:04:49.11,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse Four Seasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.37,0:05:01.60,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed that you're still \Nstanding after that attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:07.40,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Now, when exactly do you plan on using \Nthat flaming shield from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.36,0:05:09.63,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:23.05,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Rage Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.10,0:05:41.54,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:43.15,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:48.15,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.62,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Raphtalia, take care of Filo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.38,0:06:09.76,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Your flame is too cold to burn me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:18.36,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Rupture-Stance Rondo: \NTortoise Shell Cracker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:24.90,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:28.23,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Even that isn't enough to bring you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.23,0:06:31.96,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing else, I see your defense \Nlives up to your title of hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.96,0:06:34.27,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, you flatter me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:39.15,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,However, your dark flame only activates \Nwith close-quarter attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:42.14,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Not when you attack from range.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.49,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,You have an ace up your sleeve, do you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.04,0:06:47.81,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold it back. Show it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:51.63,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Very well, if you insist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:53.17,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:57.15,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Change Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.21,0:07:19.29,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,It's even less potent than \NI thought it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:22.59,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:24.81,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Such a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:28.53,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is there... Is there nothing we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.39,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,The time limit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.55,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect to hit it so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.55,0:07:40.71,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,When I give the sign, use light magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:47.61,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,The battle of the Wave \Nwill end in our victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.61,0:07:50.06,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing against you, \Nbut it is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.34,0:07:51.45,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:52.70,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Fast Light!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:57.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Fast Heal!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:00.75,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:02.65,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Of all the futile...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:21.91,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama! She's attacking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.92,0:08:28.61,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Air Strike Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.37,0:08:52.59,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,So I can't defeat him at this range.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.65,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,I shall leave this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.65,0:08:57.76,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,but you won't survive our next\N encounter unless you get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:04.63,main,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,Remember that we shall be the ones \Nto emerge triumphant from the Waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:22.27,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.68,0:09:33.83,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Did we manage to get away somehow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.58,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,That countdown showed up out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:54.24,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It must've been signaling \Nthe end of the Wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:57.78,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,But what are the Waves, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.06,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't they supposed to be \Nworld-ending calamities?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:05.88,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,That Glass woman was fixated \Non defeating me, a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.95,0:10:09.99,flashback,Glass,0000,0000,0000,,...the true battle of the Wave?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.28,0:10:16.29,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,All these questions, and no answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:22.23,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,But one thing's for sure: we must grow\Nmuch stronger by the next Wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:25.08,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't, we'll die for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:29.94,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Feeding my shield monster fragments \Nwill let me obtain new skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.05,0:10:36.64,sign_15083_92_Soul_Eater_Shiel,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(148,422)}Soul Eater Shield
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:35.63,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,but any concrete improvement will require \NRaphtalia and Filo to get class upgrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.38,main,Ake,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um, Sir Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.69,0:10:44.84,main,RK,0000,0000,0000,,You are to report to the castle at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:46.97,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:50.36,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Shield Prison!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.58,0:10:53.98,flashback,N,0000,0000,0000,,Change Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.88,0:11:02.20,flashdoublespeak,N,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Maiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:22.54,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,I saw what happened through \Nthe crystal ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.54,0:11:25.45,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,You did well to quell the Wave,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.45,0:11:27.54,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,as much as I hate to admit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.95,0:11:30.62,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really how you thank someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.28,0:11:33.51,flashback,Ake,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Sir Hero!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:35.08,flashback,Ake,0000,0000,0000,,I know how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:37.81,flashback,Ake,0000,0000,0000,,but please go with the Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:43.87,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,I have a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.87,0:11:47.30,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,How did you obtain such strength?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.93,0:11:51.66,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,You possess power unbecoming \Nof the Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:54.41,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,It is your duty to reveal \Nthe secret behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:59.80,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Now, spit it out. \NAnd don't you dare lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.73,0:12:05.25,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to know so badly,\Nkneel before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.22,0:12:13.50,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,In my world, one grovels before the \Nperson they're asking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:19.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,And they say, "I beg you. \NPlease enlighten my ignorant self."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.07,0:12:20.21,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,You cur!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.77,0:12:25.83,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,As I am now, I could kill you here and \Nwalk out the front door if I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.79,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,You're bluffing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:35.51,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do any of you here want to fight me,\Nthe man who killed the Wave's boss monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:48.72,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm willing to cooperate with you until \Nthe Waves die down and I can go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:51.92,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,So don't ever bother me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:57.99,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the king! You cannot \Ndisrespect me this way, Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.60,0:13:01.37,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.37,0:13:05.90,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have your wretched slaves \Npay for your crimes, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.50,0:13:12.83,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Use all the dirty, \Nunderhanded tricks you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:15.93,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I will protect my party through it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:19.02,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never take anything from me again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.63,0:13:22.16,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I dare you to lay a finger on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:27.48,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chase you to the ends of the earth \Nand make you regret ever being born.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:37.84,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Accursed Shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.02,0:13:50.75,main,Shadow,0000,0000,0000,,You did splendidly well \Nthis time, I daresay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.92,0:13:57.68,main,Shadow,0000,0000,0000,,Your efforts have become impossible \Nfor anyone to ignore...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:14:03.74,main,Shadow,0000,0000,0000,,Including powers who don't take too \Nkindly to you, Sir Shield Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:09.60,main,Shadow,0000,0000,0000,,Virtuous on the surface,\Nconniving and conspiring behind the scenes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:14.22,main,Shadow,0000,0000,0000,,You should exercise the utmost \Ncaution going forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:15.90,main,Shadow,0000,0000,0000,,I daresay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:22.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,"Daresay"?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.25,0:14:27.15,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Melty!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:28.37,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.08,0:14:34.76,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you spoke with \Nthe Shield Hero just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:40.39,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,And also that your talk ended \Nin a very hostile manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:47.58,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Father, if you remain at \Nodds with the Shield Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:52.26,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,we may lose our means to fight the Waves, \Nwhich could threaten our country's safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.69,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Please try to reconcile.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:56.91,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Reconcile with that swine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:00.96,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, I'm not angry at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:06.00,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you hate the Shield Hero so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.63,0:15:08.19,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.98,0:15:13.67,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,If I let him and the demi-humans do as \Nthey please, I'll yet again lose my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.04,0:15:15.45,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:18.39,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Your defiance is an affront.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:23.54,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,With the queen away, \Nthe king's word is final.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:27.36,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,And even we princesses cannot overturn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:28.81,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:31.42,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Our father is the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.27,0:15:35.13,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Whether you understand \Nhis decisions or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.13,0:15:37.37,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,they're all for the \Nbetterment of our country.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.71,0:15:42.73,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're still at an age \Nwhere you want him to baby you,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.73,0:15:46.66,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,but you should learn to \Nhold back a little, Melty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:49.87,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Just a word of advice as your older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.34,0:15:52.82,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate your concern,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.82,0:15:55.76,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,but this is none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.19,0:16:02.46,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Mother and Father, I want \Nthe best for our country, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.46,0:16:07.43,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,And it is my job as \Ncrown princess to see to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:10.66,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Melty, you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.30,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take my leave now, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.65,0:16:18.77,main,Aul,0000,0000,0000,,Melty...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.77,0:16:19.78,main,Myne,0000,0000,0000,,Papa...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.04,0:16:45.90,main,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you actually went \Nshopping for a fight with the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:49.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong. {\i1}He{\i0} picked a fight with {\i1}me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:52.62,main,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I've got everything ya need. \NDo all your shopping here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:56.15,main,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what are you going \Nto do about class upgrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.51,0:17:01.31,main,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,From what you just said, I doubt they'll \Nlet you use the dragon hourglass here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.71,0:17:05.36,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking of going to either \NSiltvelt or Shieldfreeden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:09.59,main,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,I always figured you'd go \Nto those places someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.59,0:17:12.17,main,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,I recommend Shieldfreeden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.64,0:17:15.67,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,The slave merchant recommended it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.01,0:17:19.10,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Said it's very welcoming to humans \Nfor a country of demi-humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:19.99,main,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:25.38,main,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,Over in Siltvelt, they can get pretty \Nextreme about demi-human supremacy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.80,0:17:28.23,main,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,But as the Shield Hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:30.57,top,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master, are we going on another trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:33.81,top,F,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:35.89,main,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,It usually takes a month by wagon,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.48,0:17:36.48,top,F,0000,0000,0000,,Trip, trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:38.52,main,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,but our fowl lassie here should \Nget you there sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:40.90,top,F,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.52,0:17:42.95,main,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get everything ya need \Nand load it on to your wagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.95,0:17:45.81,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I'd like a new sword for Raphtalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:47.43,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have a spare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.43,0:17:48.54,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.54,0:17:50.33,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,This will be another long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:51.93,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We should save money where we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.02,0:17:58.73,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to leave so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:01.98,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Elhart-san always works fast, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:03.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.47,0:18:10.42,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,Kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:13.77,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,I got you some gifts for the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:15.95,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,Use 'em if ya like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:19.32,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,For the kid, a shield accessory.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:24.38,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,It can analyze a shield and \Ndo tons of other useful stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:26.75,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,For the missy, a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:30.24,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same make as the one she broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:32.55,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing beats a trusty old friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:35.16,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,There's another for the missy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:36.67,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,A mana sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:39.93,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,Use it on enemies with no physical form.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.21,0:18:44.85,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,If, God forbid,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:49.25,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,the fowl lassie can't draw the wagon anymore,\N this item will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.45,0:18:52.87,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,Put this on, and gain the \Nstrength of a hundred men!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.87,0:18:54.93,italics,Elh,0000,0000,0000,,Even you could draw the wagon, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.57,0:19:14.47,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hod...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:17.85,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I love traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.34,0:19:20.59,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me free, shackled by no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:24.22,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have to deal with royalty \Nor the other heroes, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.22,0:19:27.71,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.16,0:19:36.88,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mel-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.27,0:19:40.95,top,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Long time no see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.75,0:19:40.07,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Filo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:43.54,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama, it may not have been for long,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.56,top,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up, Mel-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:46.11,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,but we traveled together as a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:45.48,top,,0000,0000,0000,,Over here, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:48.16,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:49.96,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan's a good girl, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.88,0:20:02.49,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Shield Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:07.60,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to return to the capital \Nand meet with King Aultcray once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:08.69,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.44,0:20:15.94,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to apologize\Nfor your conduct and reconcile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.94,0:20:16.98,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:23.32,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,We need your help to stop the Waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:27.95,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Also, you would be lost without \Nthe king's financial support.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.45,0:20:29.68,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Support?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.09,0:20:35.09,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one graciously working with \Nyou lot until the Waves are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.05,0:20:39.51,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,Naofumi-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.66,0:20:42.31,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,She's royalty, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:44.29,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:49.05,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,Why do both you and my father \Nhave to be like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.25,0:20:54.93,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,A hero and the king can't be fighting \Namong themselves! Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.93,0:20:56.14,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Mel-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.14,0:20:58.17,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree, Filo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.17,0:20:59.08,main,F,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.08,0:21:00.91,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,You agree too, don't you, Raphtalia-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.22,0:21:05.12,main,R,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I am Naofumi-sama's sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.12,0:21:07.94,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,See? They're agreeing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.94,0:21:09.28,main,N,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, they're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:12.19,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Look, just apologize to Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.19,0:21:15.41,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, Mother will yell at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:19.21,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,The way she throws a tantrum \Nis just like her dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.83,0:21:23.18,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Her {\i0}mother{\i1} will yell at him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.62,0:21:25.79,main,Mel,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me when I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.45,0:21:38.75,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:41.56,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:45.45,italics,N,0000,0000,0000,,It reeks of a setup!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:57.63,main,Melt,0000,0000,0000,,So return to the capital—
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.27,0:23:40.01,sign_81788_789_Walking_Over_Cor,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(356,1)}The Devil of the Shield
